---
title: Creamy Beef and Mushroom Linguine with thyme and sprinkled cheese
description: Rich and fabulously filling, this creamy beef and mushroom pasta is simple to make and full of flavour. Beef and mushrooms add wonderful texture, while thyme and muscat add depth of flavour to cut through the velvety sauce.
